graph LR
    TrustyAI[TrustyAI Service Operator]

    %% External Platform Dependencies
    TrustyAI -->|platform runtime| K8s[Kubernetes/OpenShift 1.19+/4.6+]
    TrustyAI -->|OAuth authentication| OAuth[OpenShift OAuth]
    TrustyAI -->|service mesh routing| Istio[Istio Service Mesh]
    TrustyAI -->|TLS certificates| ServiceCA[OpenShift service-ca]
    TrustyAI -.->|alternative certs| CertManager[cert-manager]
    TrustyAI -->|metrics scraping| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator]
    TrustyAI -->|job queueing| Kueue[Kueue v0.6+]

    %% External Data Dependencies
    TrustyAI -.->|optional storage| PostgreSQL[PostgreSQL/MySQL]
    TrustyAI -->|evaluation results| S3[S3-compatible Storage]
    TrustyAI -->|model downloads| HuggingFace[Hugging Face Hub]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    TrustyAI -->|model monitoring| KServe[KServe]
    TrustyAI -->|payload injection| ModelMesh[ModelMesh Serving]
    TrustyAI -.->|PVC sharing| DSP[Data Science Pipelines]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|creates resources| TrustyAI
    TrustyAI -->|monitors| KServe
    TrustyAI -->|configures| ModelMesh

    %% Service Outputs
    TrustyAI -->|exposes metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus]
    TrustyAI -->|external access| Router[OpenShift Router]
    TrustyAI -->|serverless routing| IstioGateway[Istio Gateway]

